Name: Simple Solution  All Day Training Pads,  For Dogs, Lavender Scent
Description:
Simple Solution  All Day Training Pads,  For Dogs, Lavender Scent


FOR DOGS OF ALL SIZES
SIZE: 58×60 CM
24 HOUR PROTECTION
ODOR NEUTRALIZER
6 LAYER ABSORBENCY
LEAKPROOF QUILTING


That perfect pad delivers the all-day dependability your busy lifestyle demands. Powered by InstaShield Technology, these lavender-scented premium dog pads hold up to 10 cups and eliminate odours to keep your home clean and smelling fresh. And they're guaranteed to work All Day!It's another Simple Solution to make pet parenting easier.
 
DIRECTIONS

Place on the floor, plastic side down and tissue side up
Introduce your dog to the pad and say a familiar command to encourage use If she doesn't relieve herself immediately, take her back several times until she is successful
When she relieves herself on the pad, reward her with a treat or enthusiastic praise 
Replace as needed


TRAINING TIPSEnsure the pad is accessible to your pet and away from her bed and food
